## Binary Benchmark: main vs PR

Measured with `hyperfine --warmup 1 --runs 6`.

Commands:
- `mc validate`
- `mc discover --format json`
- `mc release --dry-run`

### Baseline fixture

Fixture: 20 packages, 50 changesets, 50 commits

